\c 14
\s Gwayana navakadzikunurwa
\p
\v 1 Zvino ndakaona, tarira, Gwayana rimire pagomo reZiyoni, rine zvuru zana namakumi mana navana, vane zita raBaba varo rakanyorwa pahuma dzavo.
\v 2 Ipapo ndakanzwa inzwi richibva kudenga senzwi remvura zhinji, uye senzwi remutinhiro mukuru; ndikanzwa inzwi ravaridzi voudimbwa vachiridza udimbwa hwavo.
\v 3 Vakaimba sezvinonzi rwaiva rwiyo rutsva pamberi pechigaro choushe, napamberi pezvisikwa zvipenyu zvina, navakuru; uyo hakuna wakagona kudzidza rwiyo, asi zvuru zana namakumi mana navana, vakadzikinurwa vachibva panyika.
\v 4 Ndivo vasina kusvibiswa navakadzi; nokuti imhandara. Ndivo avo vanotevera Gwayana kose kwarinoenda. Ndivo vakadzikinurwa kubva pakati pavanhu, zvibereko zvokutanga kuna Mwari nokuGwayana.
\v 5 Mumuromo mavo hamuna kuwanikwa kunyengera, nokuti havana chavangapomerwa pamberi pechigaro choushe chaMwari.
\s Vatumwa vanozivisa kutonga kwaMwari
\p
\v 6 Zvino ndakavona mumwe mutumwa achibhururuka pakati pedenga, ane evhangeri isingaperi, kuti aiparidzire avo vanogara panyika, nekumarudzi, nendudzi, nendimi, navanhu.
\v 7 Achiti nenzwi guru: Ityai Mwari, mumurumbidzei; nokuti nguva yokutonga kwake yasvika; namatai iye wakasika denga nenyika negungwa nezvitubu zvemvura.
\v 8 ipapo mumwe mutumwa wakatevera achiti: Rawa, Rawa, Bhabhironi, guta guru, rakamwisa marudzi ose waini yokutsamwa koupombwe hwaro.
\v 9 Ipapo mutumwa wechitatu wakavatevera achiti nenzwi guru: Kana pane unonamata chikara nomufananidzo wacho, nokugamuchira chiratidzo pahuma yake kana paruvoko rwake.
\v 10 ndiye uchamwawo waini yokutsamwa kwaMwari, yakadirwa isina kuvhenganiswa mumukombe wehasha dzake; uchatambudzwa nemoto nesarufa pamberi pavatumwa vatsvene, napamberi peGwayana.
\v 11 Utsi hwokurwadziwa kwavo hwunokwira nokusingaperi peri; zvekare havana zororo masikati nousiku ivo vanonamata chikara nomufananidzo wacho, nani nani unogamuchira chiratidzo chezita racho.
\v 12 Ndipo panokutsungirira kwavatsvene, ndivo vanochengeta mirairo yaMwari nokutenda kwaJesu.
\v 13 Zvino ndakanzwa inzwi richibva kudenga richiti kwandiri: Nyora, \add uti\add*: Vakaropafadzwa vakafa, vanofira muna IShe kubva zvino. Hongu, ndizvo zvinotaura Mweya, kuti vazorore pakushingaira kwavo, nemabasa avo anovatevera.
\v 14 Ipapo ndakaona, tarira, gore jena, napamusoro pegore pakagara wakaita soMwanakomana womunhu, ane korona yendarama pamusoro wake, naparuvoko rwake jeko rinopinza.
\v 15 Zvino mumwe mutumwa wakabuda mutembere, achidanidzira nenzwi guru kuna iye wakanga agere pamusoro pegore, \add achiti\add*: Tumai jeko renyu mukohwe; nokuti nguva yokuti mukohwe yasvika, nokuti kukohwa kwenyika kwaibva.
\v 16 Ipapo wakanga agere pamusoro pegore akakandira jeko rake panyika, nyika ikakohwewa.
\v 17 Zvino mumwe mutumwa wakabuda mutembere iri kudenga, naiyewo ane jeko rinopinza.
\v 18 Nomumwe mutumwa akabuda muaritari, wakanga ane simba pamusoro pomoto, akadanidzira nenzwi guru kuna iye wakanga ane jeko rinopinza, achiti: Tumai jeko renyu rinopinza, muunganidze masumbu omuzambiringa wenyika, nokuti mazambiringa awo aibva.
\v 19 Ipapo mutumwa wakakandira jeko rake panyika, akaunganidza mazambiringa enyika, akakandira muchisviniro chewaini chikuru chokutsamwa kwaMwari.
\v 20 Asi chisvinuro chewaini chakatsikwa kunze kweguta, ropa rikabuda muchisvinuro chewaini rikasvika pamatomu amabhiza, rikasvika mastadhia* anechuru chinamazana matanhatu.
